OL,3,CBritish rivers at risk of becoming
OL,4,C'dead zones' due to chicken pollution
OL,6,FA charity says rivers in at least
OL,7,Fseven counties - where chicken
OL,8,Fproduction is highest - are at risk of
OL,9,Fbecoming dead - devoid of fish and
OL,10,Fwildlife. ITV News West of England
OL,11,FReporter Sangita Lal reports
OL,13,FRivers in at least seven counties
OL,14,Facross the UK are at risk of becoming
OL,15,Fdead zones depleted of wildlife if the
OL,16,Fgovernment does not ban new factory
OL,17,Fchicken farms, according to a new Soil
OL,18,FAssociation (SA) report shared with
OL,19,FITV News.
