OL,3,CBritish rivers at risk of becoming
OL,4,C'dead zones' due to chicken pollution
OL,6,FThe charity issued the warning in the
OL,7,Fwake of its analysis, which showed the
OL,8,Fchicken meat sector in England and
OL,9,FWales has been rising by one million
OL,10,Fbirds per month for the last decade.
OL,12,FTen rivers across the UK have been
OL,13,Fidentified by the SA as currently
OL,14,Fbeing at risk, if the number of
OL,15,Fintensive poultry units continues to
OL,16,Frise.
