OL,3,CBritish rivers at risk of becoming
OL,4,C'dead zones' due to chicken pollution
OL,6,FAs a result, the British government is
OL,7,Fbeing urged to introduce a UK-wide ban
OL,8,Fon new intensive poultry units and
OL,9,Fgive support to farmers to enable them
OL,10,Fto leave a "damaging" and "impossible
OL,11,Fto regulate" industry.
OL,13,FWhat rivers are at risk?
OL,15,FThe SA report says the following
OL,16,Frivers are at risk from the boom of
OL,17,Fintensive poultry units:
