OL,4,C'dead zones' due to chicken pollution
OL,6,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,7,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,8,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,9,FYou Need To Know...
OL,11,FSo-called dead zones are created in
OL,12,Frivers when chicken manure is washed
OL,13,Finto waterways, raising the level of
OL,14,Fphosphate.
OL,16,FIf this level becomes too high, then
OL,17,Fit creates algal blooms, which
OL,18,Fsuffocate plant life and starve
OL,19,Fwildlife that depend on it.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
