OL,6,F"And that will deoxygenate the river
OL,7,Fovernight and that will kill things."
OL,9,FSoil Association Campaign Advisor
OL,10,FCathy Cliff authored a report - titled
OL,11,FStop Killing Our Rivers - which looked
OL,12,Fat the escalating number of permits
OL,13,Ffor factory chicken farms in the UK.
OL,15,FHer study found these permits are
OL,16,Fconcentrated in river catchments
OL,17,Facross England and Wales.
