OL,6,FMs Cliff told ITV News: "We're worried
OL,7,Fthat we're going to see what's
OL,8,Fhappened to the River Wye happen to
OL,9,Fother rivers around the UK.
OL,11,F"And what we need is much more
OL,12,Fgovernment support for nature friendly
OL,13,Ffarming and that's why the Soil
OL,14,FAssociation is calling for that and
OL,15,Falso for a moratorium ban on new
OL,16,Fintensive chicken farms."
